<div class="row">
  <section id="intro" data-speed="4" data-type="background">
    <h1 class="col-sm-offset-1 title">MobileJS</h1>
    <h2 class="col-sm-offset-1 subtitle">by BarcelonaJS <a href="http://barcelonajs.org"><img class="header-logo" src="/assets/images/logo.png" alt="logo" /></a></h2>
    <div class="mostimportant">
      <span class="when">24. May 2014</span><br />
      <span class="where">Mobile World Centre, C/ de Fontanella, 2, Barcelona</span>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix intro">
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4">
        <p>A one day conference about the JavaScript mobile revolution. Talks, demos, workshops, expert tables with test devices, and more packed into a single day of JavaScript awesomeness.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4">
        <p>Una conferència d'un dia sobre les possibilitats del JavaScript a l'entorn mòbil. Hi haurà xerrades, demos, tallers i llocs de trobada amb experts que mostraran en viu diferents dispositius mòbils amb l'última tecnologia JavaScript.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4">
        <p>Una conferencia de un día, con motivo de la revolución móvil, usando JavaScript como vehículo de desarrollo; habrán charlas, demos, tallers y mesas de expertos con dispositivos y mas, todo en un dia de JavaScript.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>

<div class="spacer row">
  <h3 class="text-center"><a href="https://ti.to/barcelonajs/mobilejs">Register here (free)</a></h3>
  <p class="text-right"><i class="fa fa-twitter"></i> @bcnjs / #mobilejs</p>
</div>

<section class="intro row">
  <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4">
    <p>Organised by BarcelonaJS for the community. Attendance is free, but tickets are required and limited.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4">
    <p>Organitzat des de BarcelonaJS per a la comunitat. L'entrada és lliure però cal registrar-se per qüestions d'aforament i logística.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4">
    <p>Organizado desde BarcelonaJS para la comunidad. La entrada es gratuita sin embargo tener un ticket será obligatorio para poder asistir.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="agenda row">
  <div class="col-xs-12">
    <h3 class="col-sm-offset-1">Agenda</h3>
    <ul class="agenda-list list-group">
      <li class="list-group-item">UX mobile patterns in Titanium, Javier Rayón</li>
      <li class="list-group-item">Connecting your Arduino through mobile networks, a practical demo, Javier Zorzano</li>
      <li class="list-group-item">Hybrid apps with Ionic, Sergio Gimeno</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="row">
  <h3 class="text-center"><a class="btn btn-info btn-lg" href="https://ti.to/barcelonajs/mobilejs">Register here (free)</a></h3>
  <p class="text-right"><i class="fa fa-twitter"></i> @bcnjs / #mobilejs</p>
</div>

<section class="speakers row">
  <div class="col-xs-12">
    <h3 class="col-sm-offset-1">Speakers</h3>
  </div>
  {{#each speakers}}
  <div class="speaker equal col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-4">
    <div class="speaker-portrait col-xs-6 col-sm-2" style="background-image: url({{portrait}});"></div>
    <div class="speaker-profile">
      <span class="speaker-name">{{name}}</span>
      <p>{{bio}}</p>
      <a href="http://twitter.com/{{twitter}}"><i class="fa fa-twitter"></i> {{twitter}}</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  {{/each}}
</section>

<div class="row">
  <h3 class="text-center"><a class="btn btn-info btn-lg" href="https://ti.to/barcelonajs/mobilejs">Register here (free)</a></h3>
  <p class="text-right"><i class="fa fa-twitter"></i> @bcnjs / #mobilejs</p>
</div>

<section class="supporters row">
  <div class="col-xs-12">
    <h3 class="col-sm-offset-1">Supporters</h3>
    {{#each supporters}}
    <div class="supporter col-xs-12 col-sm-4 text-center">
      <a href="{{url}}"><img class="supporter-logo" src="{{logo}}" alt={{name}} /></a>
    </div>
    {{/each}}
    <div class="col-xs-12"><p>We're currently looking for supporters. Interested? <a href="mailto:mobile@barcelonajs.org">Get in touch</a>.</p></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="speakers row">
  <div class="col-xs-12">
    <h3 class="col-sm-offset-1">Workshops & More</h3>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="team row">
  <div class="col-xs-12">
    <h3 class="col-sm-offset-1">Team</h3>
  </div>
  {{#each team}}
  <div class="member equal col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-6">
    <div class="member-portrait col-xs-6 col-sm-2" style="background-image: url({{portrait}});"></div>
    <div class="member-profile">
      <span class="member-name">{{name}}</span>
      <p>{{bio}}</p>
      <a href="http://twitter.com/{{twitter}}"><i class="fa fa-twitter"></i> {{twitter}}</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  {{/each}}
</section>

<section class="meta row">
  <div class="col-xs-12 text-center">
    <h4>A BarcelonaJS event. <a href="http://barcelonajs.org/code">Code of Conduct</a></h4>
  </div>
